  "response_text": "A dark, blue-tinted computer-style display fills the screen, as if seen through a robot’s targeting system. A large ant appears magnified against a textured background, its pale legs and golden body segments clearly visible. The words “SEARCH MODE” glow in the upper left, with a thin rectangular targeting border, small corner markers, and stacked indicator bars along the side. The view changes to a dim kitchen interior still overlaid with the same search graphics. Cabinets, a countertop, a coffee maker, bottles, and small appliances sit along the right side, while the floor stretches into the foreground. A glowing orange trail curves across the kitchen floor, dotted with tiny dark specks that suggest a line of ants moving through the room.\n\nA doorway opens into a smoky, backlit space. A huge, dark humanoid robot silhouette stands in the doorway, broad-shouldered with oversized arms and heavy mechanical legs. Bright light shines from behind it, creating a dramatic outline. As it steps forward, small lights on its body and head begin to glow, and a horizontal flare of light crosses its chest and face. The robot’s bulky body fills the doorway, framed by the open doors and blue haze.\n\nThe robot is then seen from the front in a larger interior space with high windows and beams of cool blue light behind it. Its upper body has a cockpit-like opening; inside is the face of an adult man, visible through the machinery. He appears to be operating or wearing the robot suit. The front of the suit includes the Orkin name on a chest panel. Mechanical arms and side panels rise around him, and small lights dot the robot’s torso.\n\nA close view of a metallic nozzle attached to the robot’s arm points outward. The nozzle resembles a small cannon or sprayer, with a round barrel and polished metal tip. A bright yellow-orange beam projects from it. The beam is shown sweeping into the kitchen area, aimed along the counter and appliances.\n\nThe display returns to a targeting view of an ant, now enlarged and partly translucent with colored internal-looking areas. A rectangular orange targeting frame and crosshairs lock over the insect. Small white text along the bottom reads, “REFUND LIMITED CALL ORKIN FOR DETAILS.” The targeting words progress to “TARGET TERMINATED,” and a large orange “GUARANTEED” appears over the ant image, reinforcing the result of the attack.\n\nThe robot faces forward again, still surrounded by blue light, with the arm-mounted sprayer extended and the yellow beam shining from it. Large white text appears across the bottom: “1 800 800 ORKIN.” As the image continues, the bulky robot exterior gives way to the real Orkin Man standing in its place. He is an adult man in a neat service uniform: a light-colored button-up shirt with a black tie, tan trousers, a dark belt, and a white cap bearing the Orkin logo. He holds pest-control equipment at his side and stands confidently against the smoky blue background. The red Orkin logo appears near him, while the large phone number “1 800 800 ORKIN” remains across the bottom. He finishes facing forward with a slight smile, one hand near his hip, presenting the service directly to the viewer.",
